  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then boil a kettle and take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge and open the packet to let it air</p><p>Add your <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (Can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a plate with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix until combined</p><p>Add your <strong>chicken thighs</strong> to the plate and turn them several times until evenly coated in all the spices</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
