    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chicken thighs</strong> and any remaining spices and cook for 3 min on each side until browned</p>",
