          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>cooked chicken thighs</strong> to a clean board and shred them apart, using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Return the <strong>shredded chicken</strong> to the dish and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>shredded</strong> <strong>chicken thigh chilli</strong></p>",
