      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>shredded</strong> <strong>chicken thigh chilli</strong> with the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong></p><p>Dollop with your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong> all over and garnish with the <strong>coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
